&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;x_elementtoproof&quot;&gt;&lt;span data-olk-copy-source=&quot;MessageBody&quot;&gt;Founded in 2008, Nextiva has grown into a global leader trusted by over 100,000 businesses and 1M+ users worldwide. Headquartered in Scottsdale, Arizona, and with teams across the globe, we&#39;re the future of customer experience and team collaboration through our AI-powered, conversation-centric platform.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
